      "id": "1017340081457079",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Idea",
      "review_description": "I know this game is supposed to be like phasmophobia so I have an idea for something that you guys could add to each of the maps! In phasmophobia, there are the cursed items or objects that start a hunt when interacted with, so I was thinking you guys could add the same thing to the free version (would be greatly appreciated because I'm a demo player), and the full game version as well. It could just be a specific item like a book, music box, or doll that either randomly spawns, or spawns in a specific room of each map. It could also have a particle effect to distinguish it from other props! It would probably make multiplayer runs way more chaotic if somebody triggers a hunt event! To prevent grieving, you could make it where the item has a cooldown or a specific amount of uses before it permanently disables. That's the only thing I wanted to suggest, sorry for the long description.😅 Keep up the good work!",
      "date": 1773545470,
