      "id": "822511647621643",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "My favorate horror game",
      "review_description": "This game is one of my favorates ever in VR. It has exotic skins, the best multiplayer experiences, and enhanced gameplay to completely replicate a well made masterpiece. It is also the scariest game I show to my friends, who also love the gameplay it has. I congratulate the skill and quality this game has to offer and I would highly recommend others to try this spectacular experience which will make you addicted for a while. Honestly, I really enjoy this game and the horror aspects it shows in the creepy maps and well designed, varried horror creatures. I can view the serious effort put into this one of a kind, brilliant example of the greatest horror game. The way it scares me it gives a sensational feeling that I am an addict of which shows to me that this game deserves the utmost gratitude from all players and more. 5 stars for the best horror experience I've ever experienced.",
